sub_title: Geologist working in the geothermal industry
summary: Graduated Geologist with a master's degree in Earth Sciences from the VU Amsterdam. Currently working in the geothermal industry as a geologist, projects involve seismic interpretation of the subsurface, petrophysical evaluation and subsidy applications. Through this work I try to contribute to a more sustainable future.
